120
00:08:12,310 --> 00:08:15,270
In the second top diagram from the left,

121
00:08:15,270 --> 00:08:20,810
conservation of charge requires that
the emitted W boson has a negative charge.

122
00:08:20,810 --> 00:08:28,600
We can only emit a negative boson.

