135
00:09:20,548 --> 00:09:25,860
The right-most diagram is
a diagram of strong interactions.

136
00:09:25,860 --> 00:09:33,260
The incoming red d quark emits a gluon and
becomes a green d quark.

137
00:09:33,260 --> 00:09:38,036
And in order to conserve color the quantum
numbers carried by the gluon must be red,

138
00:09:38,036 --> 00:09:38,935
anti-green.

139
00:09:43,614 --> 00:09:48,071
On the other hand, the gluon is
not able to change the flavor of

140
00:09:48,071 --> 00:09:52,635
the particles such that the d
quark must indeed stay at d quark.

